            <h1>Parking at UC San Diego</h1> <br>
            <div class="information">
                <p><b>If you wish to park at UC San Diego, you will need to purchase parking in order to support construction, maintenance, and the adminstration of parking facilities. You must have a valid permit? during these hours: </b></p>

                <!-- guidelines -->
                <div class="guidelines">
                    <ul> 
                        <li>Main campus — 7 a.m. to 11 p.m. weekdays</li>
                        <li>Scripps Institution of Oceanography — 7 a.m. to 11 p.m., 7 days a week</li>
                        <li>Medical Center Hillcrest — 24 hours/ 7 days a week</li>
                        <li>Medical Center La Jolla — 24 hours/ 7 days a week</li>
                        <li>No parking fee is required on university holidays, or during these off-peak hours:
                            <ul>
                                <li>Main campus – A, B, S, V, VP, and metered spaces from 11 p.m. to 7 a.m. weekdays and all day Saturdays and Sundays</li>
                                <li>Scripps Institution of Oceanography – A, B, and S spaces from 11 p.m. to 7 a.m., 7 days a week</li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div> 
                <!-- End of guidelines -->

                <br>
                <p><b>Select parking type to view information</b> <br><br>
                    
                    <!-- V Spot Button -->
                    <button id="v-btn" class="btn btn-info">V (Visitor)</button></p>
                    
                    <!-- V Spot -->
                    <div class="v">
                        Rates
                        <ul>
                            <li>H$1/45 minutes </li>
                            <li>$8/day </li>
                        </ul>
                        With purchase of a V spot, you may park in the following spaces: 
                        <ul>
                            <li><font color="grey"><b>V</b></font>: 24 hours daily</li>
                            <li><font color="yellow"><b>S</b></font>: 24 hours daily</li>
                            <li><font color="green"><b>B</b></font>: 24 hours daily
                                <ul>
                                    <li>Valid in lot P207 4:30 p.m. – 7:30 a.m. only</li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                            <li><font color="red"><b>A</b></font>: 4:30 p.m. – 7:30 a.m. daily
                                <ul>
                                    <li>Not valid where posted “A permit required 24 hours a day, 7 days a week”</li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                            <li>Meters (with no fee): 4:30 p.m. – 7:30 a.m. daily</li>
                            <li>Never valid in: Lots P406, P411, P603, P604, Gilman Parking Structure,  Hopkins Parking Structure, and Pangea Parking Structure</li>
                        </div> 
                        <!-- End of V Spot-->

                        <!-- VP Spot Button -->
                        <p><button id="vp-btn" class="btn btn-info">VP (Visitor Premium)</button></p>

                        <!-- VP Spot -->
                        <div class="vp">
                            Rates
                            <ul>
                                <li>$2/hour</li>
                                <li>$16/day</li>
                            </ul>
                            With purchase of a VP spot, you may park in the same spaces as those who purchase a V spot along with access to parking in lots:
                            <ul>
                                <li><font color="red"><b>VP</b></font>: 24 hours daily</li>
                                <li>P406, P411, P603</li>
                                <li>Gilman Parking Structure</li>
                                <li>Hopkins Parking Structure</li>
                                <li>Pangea Parking Structure</li>
                                <li> Never valid in lot P604</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <!-- End of VP Spot -->
                        
                    </div> 
                    <!-- End of information --> 

                </div>

                <script>
                $('#v-btn').click(function(){
                  $('.v').animate({
                    left: "+=500",
